title: Michele Greene (Abby Perkins on LA Law) 2 albums MP3
description:
Here are two albums by Michele Green who played Abby Perkins
on L.A. Law which, for you youngsters, was a big hit on TV
twentysome years ago.  She sings in Spanish and English equally
well and her voice is beautiful and unique.

I'm posting them in three formats: Flac, Mp3, and Wave with a
cue.  EAC extraction logs are included with all of them, as
well as scans of the jewel case art.

I hope you enjoy these obscure little treasures.
